<h1>Don't Forget Your Blind Repair! 📦</h1>

<p>Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>

<div class="highlight-box">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #856404;">⏰ Gentle Reminder</h3>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">We noticed you haven't shipped your blinds yet for <strong>Order #<%= String.pad_leading(to_string(@order.id), 6, "0") %></strong>. To get your blinds repaired and back to perfect working condition, please ship them to us as soon as possible.</p>
</div>

<h3>Your Order Details:</h3>
<%= if length(@order.order_line_items) > 0 do %>
    <%= for line_item <- @order.order_line_items do %>
        <ul style="padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
            <li><strong>Blind Type:</strong> <%= String.capitalize(line_item.blind_type) %></li>
            <li><strong>Dimensions:</strong> <%= line_item.width %>" × <%= line_item.height %>"</li>
            <li><strong>Quantity:</strong> <%= line_item.quantity %></li>
        </ul>
    <% end %>
<% end %>
<ul style="padding-left: 20px;">
    <li><strong>Service Level:</strong> <%= String.capitalize(@order.service_level) %></li>
    <li><strong>Total Price:</strong> $<%= @order.total_price %></li>
</ul>

<div class="info-box">
    <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">📍 Ship Your Blinds To:</h3>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; margin: 10px 0;">
        <strong>Blind Restoration</strong><br>
        11034 Island CT.<br>
        Allendale, MI 49401
    </p>
    <div style="background: #fff3cd; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px; margin-top: 15px;">
        <strong>Important:</strong> Include Order #<%= String.pad_leading(to_string(@order.id), 6, "0") %> on the package
    </div>
</div>

<h3>Need Help?</h3>
<p>We're here to make shipping easy:</p>
<ul style="padding-left: 20px;">
    <li>📋 View our detailed <a href="<%= BlindShopWeb.Endpoint.url() %>/shipping-instructions" style="color: #f59e0b;">shipping instructions</a></li>
    <li>📧 Reply to this email with any questions</li>
    <li>📞 Call us at 1-800-BLINDFIX</li>
</ul>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <a href="<%= BlindShopWeb.Endpoint.url() %>/shipping-instructions" class="button button-primary">View Shipping Instructions</a>
</div>

<p style="color: #666; font-style: italic;">
    Remember: The sooner you ship, the sooner you'll have your perfectly working blinds back!
</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>
The BlindRestoration Team</p>
